<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= __('lang') %>" dir="<%= __('dir') %>">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= __('title_privacy') %></title>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 Grid System ONLY -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap-grid.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Styles -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    
    <style>
        .legal-header {
            padding: 20vh 0 10vh;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xxl);
        }
        .legal-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            padding-bottom: var(--spacing-xxl);
        }
        .legal-content h2 {
            color: var(--color-text-primary);
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin: var(--spacing-xl) 0 var(--spacing-md);
            font-family: var(--font-serif);
        }
        .legal-content h3 {
            color: var(--color-text-primary);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0 var(--spacing-sm);
        }
        .legal-content p {
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
        }
        .legal-content ul {
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
            padding-left: var(--spacing-lg);
        }
        .legal-content li {
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="theme-dark">
    <!-- Custom Cursor -->
    <div class="cursor-dot"></div>
    <div class="cursor-outline"></div>

    <header class="navbar scrolled">
        <div class="navbar-container">
            <a href="/" class="brand-logo">KURD CUT</a>
            <div class="nav-actions">
                <a href="/" class="btn-secondary"><%= __('nav_return') %></a>
            </div>
            <button class="mobile-menu-toggle">
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <div class="legal-header text-center fade-up">
            <h1 class="hero-title" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);"><%= __('privacy_title') %></h1>
            <p class="section-subtitle"><%= __('privacy_eff') %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-content fade-up delay-1">
            <p>At Kurd Cut, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it through our compliance with this policy. This policy describes the types of information we may collect from you or that you may provide when you visit the Kurd Cut website or use our mobile application, and our practices for collecting, using, maintaining, protecting, and disclosing that information.</p>

            <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect several types of information from and about users of our Platform, including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Personal Data:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and location (for Customer booking accounts).</li>
                <li><strong>Business Data:</strong> Shop name, addresses, service menus, team members, and financial transaction metadata (for Business accounts).</li>
                <li><strong>Usage Details:</strong> IP addresses, browser information, and details of your visits to our Platform.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use information that we collect about you or that you provide to us:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>To present our Platform and its contents to you in the highest quality.</li>
                <li>To facilitate and manage bookings between Customers and Businesses.</li>
                <li>To process subscription payments for Business Shop accounts securely.</li>
                <li>To notify you about changes to our Platform or any products or services we offer.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. Data Security</h2>
            <p>We have implemented world-class measures designed to secure your personal information from accidental loss and from unauthorized access, use, alteration, and disclosure. All information you provide to us is stored on our secure servers behind deep-encryption firewalls.</p>

            <h2>4. Contact Information</h2>
            <p>To ask questions or comment about this privacy policy and our privacy practices, contact us at: <a href="mailto:privacy@kurdcut.com" class="btn-link">privacy@kurdcut.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container footer-grid">
            <div class="footer-brand">
                <h2>KURD CUT</h2>
                <p><%= __('footer_slogan') %></p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <div class="link-group">
                    <h4><%= __('footer_platform') %></h4>
                    <a href="/#discover"><%= __('nav_discover') %></a>
                    <a href="/business-subscription"><%= __('nav_business') %></a>
                </div>
                <div class="link-group">
                    <h4><%= __('footer_company') %></h4>
                    <a href="/terms"><%= __('footer_terms') %></a>
                    <a href="/privacy"><%= __('footer_privacy') %></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p><%- __('footer_copyright') %></p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
